<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>404 - Sayfa Bulunamadı</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6A11CB, #2575FC);
            color: #fff;
        }
        .container {
            text-align: center;
            max-width: 600px;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }
        h1 {
            font-size: 80px;
            margin: 0;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        h2 {
            font-size: 24px;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }
        p {
            font-size: 16px;
            margin: 10px 0 20px;
        }
        a {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #fff;
            background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-weight: bold;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, transform 0.2s ease;
        }
        a:hover {
            background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
            transform: scale(1.05);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>404</h1>
        <h2>Sayfa Bulunamadı</h2>
        <p>Aradığınız sayfa bulunamadı. Yanlış bir bağlantı kullanmış olabilirsiniz ya da sayfa kaldırılmış olabilir.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
